00:28:17.972 --> 00:28:18.470
PROFESSOR: Yeah.

00:28:18.470 --> 00:28:20.265
And not so much convincing
things that

00:28:20.265 --> 00:28:22.740
it's their idea it's--

00:28:22.740 --> 00:28:25.430
yeah, I don't want to phrase it
