who will wait to see

00:30:31.005 --> 00:30:33.830
and will sort of sit
on the fence but

00:30:33.830 --> 00:30:42.005
[INAUDIBLE], but open.

00:30:42.005 --> 00:30:43.694
They have other priorities,
but they're open to

00:30:43.694 --> 00:30:46.380
