00:46:12.278 --> 00:46:13.274
[INAUDIBLE]

00:46:13.274 --> 00:46:16.262
much more [INAUDIBLE]
than [INAUDIBLE].

00:46:23.234 --> 00:46:24.728
PROFESSOR: That may be true.

